&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Rethinking Superiority in Customer-Vendor Relationships 
    &lt;div id=&#34;rethinking-superiority-in-customer-vendor-relationships&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
